      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PAW NIALL (5) latest effort finished 2nd on March 31 over 410m at this track behind Doongalla Jessie beaten 7 lengths (23.41) in a Grade 5. Looks suited here and rates on top. IS HE LUCKY (3) is struggling to break through but racing consistently, finishing in the minors three starts on end. Last time out flew the lids with a fast early sectional but gathered in and finished in the minors when third (23.46) at this track over 410m. Goes well out of this box with a win and four minor placings. Overdue and is among the main hopes. RIGHTEOUS FURY (8) was below best at his last start when 6th at this track following a third place finish (22.21) at Shepparton two back. Goes well out of this box with a win and three minor placings. Has ability and is one of the better chances. WAXING (1) generally performs well over this distance.",
